<br>
I heard that the 5-7 day wait on the Ragefire spawn was actually an error in the code and that they were working on getting it back to 72 hours +/- whatever, like the old Ragefire spawn in Sol B was.<br>
<br>
The other parts of the cleric quest are pretty easy and could be accomplished in 1 day if you planned it right. Lowering the Ragefire spawn to 10 hours would make it so you really could complete the epic in 1 day and i don't think that is really what Verant had in mind when they came up with these mega quests that were supposed to keep you busy for a weeks and give you an awesome prize at the end.<br>
<br>
That's just my opinion, but maybe that is because it took me 8 months to complete my epic (/thanks all those in AdA that helped, especially Talania!!)....I guess it is selfish, but it took a lot of hard work to get my epic, and i would be kinda miffed if it could now be accomplished in 1 day.<br>
